	(42, 8, 1, '', '2015-02-08 09:52:58', 135, 3246, '2822f7c60285072f070fedf4b205f5c95c108f49', '{"id":8,"asset_id":"72","title":"Metallica - European Summer Vacation Part 612","alias":"peter-tries-one-more","introtext":"<p>We just finished celebrating Halloween, so it must be about time to talk summer festivals, right?(!) This year we are kicking off the annual European summer vacation announcements in unchartered waters as we\'re psyched to be hitting the stage at three brand new festivals in Germany and Austria. We\'ll be headlining, along with our friends Muse and KISS, at these three day extravaganzas now a part of this summer tradition in Europe:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>May, 29-31: N\\u00fcrburg, Germany at <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.der-ring.de\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Der Ring - Gr\\u00fcne H\\u00f6lle Rock<\\/a> and Munich, Germany at <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rockavaria.de\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Rockavaria Festival<\\/a> June, 4-6: Vienna, Austria at <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rockinvienna.at\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Rock in Vienna<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tickets go on sale tomorrow, November 6th at 9 AM in Vienna, 10 AM for the two German shows. Pick up tickets for Vienna at <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.ticketmaster.at\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Ticketmaster.at<\\/a> and for the German shows at <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.ticketmaster.de\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Ticketmaster.de<\\/a>. Since these are general admission festivals, there will not be a Met Club presale.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Stay tuned... we will definitely be back before the holidays with a few additions to our annual trek!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"articles\\/der-ring-grune-holle-rock.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/> <img src=\\"articles\\/rock-in-vienna.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/> <img src=\\"articles\\/rockavaria.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2015-02-03 15:52:04","created_by":"136","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-02-08 09:52:58","modified_by":"135","checked_out":"135",